50:00.148 --> 50:02.227
This whole mess is my fault.

50:08.060 --> 50:09.318
It's definitely your fault.

50:09.319 --> 50:11.176
Come on, Charlie.

50:11.177 --> 50:12.116
But look at us.

50:12.117 --> 50:14.713
