50:48.420 --> 50:52.037
He was so proud of you, Gerry.
Because you'd won.

50:52.076 --> 50:57.551
You made Twirl! The 'Karate
Kid' of baton twirling films.

50:57.831 --> 51:01.168
So if we lose the house, it's okay.

51:01.307 --> 51:03.785
