51:33.155 --> 51:34.134
He doesn't sound very healthy.

51:34.135 --> 51:36.173
He's probably in character.

51:36.672 --> 51:39.190
We should probably get him out of sight.
Come on!

51:41.926 --> 51:43.144
That's a great idea!

51:43.145 --> 51:45.901
Yeah, yeah! Go inside and
lay low until we're ready!

51:45.902 --> 51:47.200
There's snacks downstairs.

51:47.201 --> 51:50.419
Hey, make yourself comfortable.
Mi casa es su casa.

52:05.922 --> 52:07.340
