52:07.341 --> 52:08.719
Wayne, I know... Paige is pissed.

52:08.720 --> 52:10.097
No, no, not you.

52:10.098 --> 52:11.776
No... Hey, Charlie. Not you.

52:11.777 --> 52:14.213
Hey, you! I know you
have feelings for Paige.

52:14.214 --> 52:15.192
Come on.

52:15.193 --> 52:17.591
Hey... hey look!

52:18.230 --> 52:20.027
I know you love her, okay?

52:20.028 --> 52:21.806
I've learned to accept that.

52:21.807 --> 52:27.701
