You know?

53:06.542 --> 53:07.101
Yeah.

53:07.102 --> 53:10.697
My special connection with vampires.

53:10.698 --> 53:14.048
I can sense their presence, you know?

53:14.049 --> 53:18.928
I mean if one was near...
it's like I could feel him...

53:18.929 --> 53:21.767
I know. It's a lot to take in.

53:28.600 --> 53:30.417
You know what? I love her.

53:30.418 --> 53:33.454
