her and you know that!

53:33.455 --> 53:34.634
Guys, maybe we should get inside.

53:34.635 --> 53:38.011
Give the guy a break!
He's pouring his heart out here.

53:38.410 --> 53:42.267
See what I mean?
It's like he doesn't even listen!

53:43.485 --> 53:46.369
Am I sparkling?

53:53.695 --> 53:56.552
Aw, man. People are
trying to leave already.

54:09.599 --> 54:11.298
I'm sorry?

54:16.592 --> 54:19.110
Was that... was that so hard?

54:21.707 --> 54:24.842
Ha ha... okay, pal.

54:24.843 --> 54:26.982
Okay. That's good.

54:29.239 --> 54:31.517
Yeah. Okay.

54:32.336 --> 54:35.192
Let's get back in there,
before we miss all the fun, right? Yeah.

54:35.193 --> 54:36.792
Okay. Okay.

54:36.931 --> 54:38.768
Hey, where'd you go?

54:38.769 --> 54:41.186
Line for the pisser was too long.

54:41.187 --> 54:44.228
And I brought my private stock.

54:50.658 --> 54:52.726
What the fuck?!

54:52.735 --> 54:55.112
